  "description": "MidStream is a powerful platform that makes AI conversations smarter and more responsive. Instead of waiting for an AI to finish speaking before understanding what it's saying, MidStream analyzes responses as they stream in real-time—enabling instant insights, pattern detection, and intelligent decision-making.",
